abstract: WESTFIELD, N.J., Nov. 11 In the Westfield Presbyterian Church this afternoon, Miss Ernestine Sabrina Coffey, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Edward Lyman Coffey, became the bride of Hugh Harding Chapman Jr. of State College, Pa., son of Mr. and Mrs. Chapman of Evansville, Ind.
headline_main: Ernestine Coffey Is Married To Hugh Harding Chapman Jr.
headline_print_headline: Ernestine Coffey Is Married To Hugh Harding Chapman Jr.
